{"tid":107634,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［齊來向成功人士學習］SpaceX & Tesla 創辦人 Elon Musk","createTime":"2017-02-04T14:52:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-08T15:48:29.000Z","uid":12731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"054f78c3fb9383c11c8828004dcef6d7de1b6346","tid":107634,"uid":12731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T14:52:46.000Z","msg":"有本書叫做Elon Musk - Tesla, SpaceX, and the Quest for a Fantastic Future<br />\n係佢嘅自傳 巴絲們有興趣可以睇下<br />\n<br />\n另外唔想睇咁多英文可以上網search下有好多關於佢嘅文章<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n開post嚟討論下 討論咩都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10ffe326915be79b4c612e5b6d384413f7e2445d","tid":107634,"uid":76379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T01:46:52.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"6ed2ee6d098a73f2cd0cc6741be1b6401cf3c8bb","tid":107634,"uid":14623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T01:50:14.000Z","msg":"本書真心好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"911454bcf80ac243070463842e21734c3b060fdd","tid":107634,"uid":76379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T03:28:07.000Z","msg":"樓主係未都會睇其他傳記<br />\n我未睇過本書亦都唔了解Elon Musk，但想知道佢性格同背景比其他人有咩特別?"},{"pid":"e98ee5cf0e84213f3679caa83f3616e535c5ed25","tid":107634,"uid":12731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T04:45:24.000Z","msg":"其實我都未睇哂本書，但有好多人介紹我睇，依家睇緊<br />\n<br />\n有無人討論下？"},{"pid":"437f0c5ee6000437bd5821609159ed34387407e4","tid":107634,"uid":15453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T12:44:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實我都未睇哂本書，但有好多人介紹我睇，依家睇緊<br />\n<br />\n有無人討論下？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb3f6f794016482c097b355bf2b7b8cfb334e9d2","tid":107634,"uid":15453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T13:07:05.000Z","msg":"10歲買電腦<br />\n神速學識打code<br />\n因為想買Game<br />\n所以自己寫咗隻game叫Blastar<br />\n賣咗500美元<br />\n個時佢12歲<br />\n(12歲個時我連飛機都未識打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nElon已經識寫一隻打飛機嘅game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n17歲去加拿大讀degree<br />\n後來又走咗去美國讀書<br />\n先後完成經濟同物理學士<br />\n<br />\n係佢讀大學嘅時候已經深信<br />\n網絡、可再生能源同大空移民<br />\n係未來有相當大嘅potential<br />\n<br />\n讀完Degree緊係去讀master<br />\n結果讀咗唔夠一個星期就quit U<br />\n<br />\nElon心諗到佢讀完master再創業就太遲<br />\n所以全心全意行自己嘅it路<br />\n<br />\n一開始同細佬(好似係)整咗Zip2<br />\n無記咗嘅話之後好似賣咗<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://之後就成立X.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E4%B9%8B%E5%BE%8C%E5%B0%B1%E6%88%90%E7%AB%8BX.com&d=Peq93FhG%2BXbpjcIFBj2O6dibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=5d8b3cdb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">之後就成立X.com</a><br />\n做到有聲有色<br />\n同另一間公司合併<br />\n改名做PayPal<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n幾年之後PayPal被eBay用15億美完收購咗<br />\nElon就得到咗一筆165M美元<br />\n個時嘅Elon只係啱啱三字出頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"886ebf93d69f625e0b98e1a6a7ce473792d246f9","tid":107634,"uid":15453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T13:09:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>10歲買電腦<br />\n神速學識打code<br />\n因為想買Game<br />\n所以自己寫咗隻game叫Blastar<br />\n賣咗500美元<br />\n個時佢12歲<br />\n(12歲個時我連飛機都未識打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nElon已經識寫一隻打飛機嘅game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n17歲去加拿大讀degree<br />\n後來又走咗去美國讀書<br />\n先後完成經濟同物理學士<br />\n<br />\n係佢讀大學嘅時候已經深信<br />\n網絡、可再生能源同大空移民<br />\n係未來有相當大嘅potential<br />\n<br />\n讀完Degree緊係去讀master<br />\n結果讀咗唔夠一個星期就quit U<br />\n<br />\nElon心諗到佢讀完master再創業就太遲<br />\n所以全心全意行自己嘅it路<br />\n<br />\n一開始同細佬(好似係)整咗Zip2<br />\n無記咗嘅話之後好似賣咗<br />\n<br />\n之後就成立<a href=\"http://X.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FX.com&d=Peq93FhG%2BXbpjcIFBj2O6dibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=939492cf\" target=\"_blank\">http://X.com</a><br />\n做到有聲有色<br />\n同另一間公司合併<br />\n改名做PayPal<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n幾年之後PayPal被eBay用15億美完收購咗<br />\nElon就得到咗一筆165M美元<br />\n個時嘅Elon只係啱啱三字出頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n之後就入戲肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講佢點用個165M<br />\n去搞SpaceX Tesla SolarCity etc <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6464a39d8cf6eff47d45c4814ec0cd711f259767","tid":107634,"uid":48579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T14:52:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>10歲買電腦<br />\n神速學識打code<br />\n因為想買Game<br />\n所以自己寫咗隻game叫Blastar<br />\n賣咗500美元<br />\n個時佢12歲<br />\n(12歲個時我連飛機都未識打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nElon已經識寫一隻打飛機嘅game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n17歲去加拿大讀degree<br />\n後來又走咗去美國讀書<br />\n先後完成經濟同物理學士<br />\n<br />\n係佢讀大學嘅時候已經深信<br />\n網絡、可再生能源同大空移民<br />\n係未來有相當大嘅potential<br />\n<br />\n讀完Degree緊係去讀master<br />\n結果讀咗唔夠一個星期就quit U<br />\n<br />\nElon心諗到佢讀完master再創業就太遲<br />\n所以全心全意行自己嘅it路<br />\n<br />\n一開始同細佬(好似係)整咗Zip2<br />\n無記咗嘅話之後好似賣咗<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://之後就成立X.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E4%B9%8B%E5%BE%8C%E5%B0%B1%E6%88%90%E7%AB%8BX.com&d=Peq93FhG%2BXbpjcIFBj2O6dibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=5d8b3cdb